➜重庆洪崖洞来广州了！说起老板，爸妈都认识…
http://www.sohu.com/a/437678586_100131509	40945
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>广州也有洪崖洞了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>还能在里面涮火锅</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>？？？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201211/160ff59e1741458b94cfb0a7d8a69f9e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">原来是胡海泉开的火锅店</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">请广州人在洪崖洞里吃火锅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201211/28e85577d8bd4fe99cdc8e9990aa8a83.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围，活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201211/946c209592ab4d42beaf31ae9ba6f09b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
